mods.abstract: ONE HUNDRED DOLLARS REWARD. Run away from the house of the subscriber, No. 207 Julia street, last February, a mulatto woman named RHODA, aged abou 35 years, common height, slender built, straight hair, bad teeth, speaks quick when spoken to, and stammers a little when speaking; looks like an Indian woman; says she is free. She is from Canton, Miss., and formerly belonged to Frisby Jones of that place. She has been seen in Carrollton and Lafayette several times since she ran off. The above reward will be paid for her delivery to me in this city. F.M. FISK. nov25 tf
